{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回\"英雄会\"中，两名戴面具的黑衣人——笑脸人与哭脸人——闯入客栈挑衅少林弟子姚长华等人，楚留香与胡铁花被迫应战。三人追至荒坟，发现四口小棺材和一口大棺材，哭脸人请二人\"吃死人\"，楚留香识破棺中不过是浇了红糖汁的白藕。面具揭晓，来人竟是新交朋友李玉函与其妻柳无眉，二人以荒诞的坟场宴席戏弄胡铁花以解闷。席间楚留香点破李玉函身份——拥翠山庄少庄主，其父李观鱼曾被誉为天下第一剑客，但十年前染病卧床。李玉函推崇薛衣人为当世第一剑，并提及楚留香揭发南宫灵与妙僧无花阴谋的壮举。柳无眉邀请二人前往拥翠山庄做客，胡铁花欣然向往，楚留香因俗务婉拒。柳无眉提及家中几位文武全才的少女急于见楚留香，其中一位名叫苏蓉蓉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "姚长华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这两位也是香帅的朋友么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非也。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "姚长华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么这两人是谁呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_yao_chang_hua",
      "text": "你怎么问起我来了?你是堂堂少林门下，又是这里的地主，地面上若有了来历不明的人，你怎会不知道?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "笑脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到这里还有少林门下，失敬了，失敬了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "久闻少林神拳天下无敌，朋友可愿意出来赐教几招么?",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "姚长华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……在下……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_jian_guang",
      "speaker_name": "毛健光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友是哪条道上的?难道不晓得住在这里的是什么人?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "笑脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来也不过是几个只会大言欺人的鼠辈而已。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_jian_guang",
      "speaker_name": "毛健光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友嘴上最好放干净些，可知道这名满天下的胡大侠和楚香帅都在这里。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我等今日正是来找胡大侠和楚香帅的，只要是这两人的朋友，也全都算上，和这两人没关系的，最好站到一边去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_jian_guang",
      "speaker_name": "毛健光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们和楚留香可没有什么关系，简直连认都不认得，是么?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "根本就不认得……谁是楚留香呀?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是一群鼠辈。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "笑脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，你们两人就出来吧!",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_mao_jian_guang",
      "text": "毛大镖客，你我多年的交情，你不帮帮我的忙么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_jian_guang",
      "speaker_name": "毛健光",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你……你是什么人，我根本不认得你，你怎能血口喷人?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_mao_jian_guang",
      "text": "你既不认得我，这杯酒就还给你吧!",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你真该改个名字，叫大嫖客还好些。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "看来你厉害的对头倒真不少。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这两人不是你的仇人么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这两人我根本连见都没有见过。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我也没见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你再想想，这两人一定是来找你的，我的仇人都没有这么好的功夫，只有一个“鬼王”韩非，但三年前也已真的做鬼了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我也想不出有这样的对头。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你连他们的身法功夫都看不出么?江湖中这样的高手并不多呀!",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这两人掌力俱阴柔已极，像是南宗的‘金丝绵掌’，但能将金丝绵掌练到这种火候的，三十年来也不过只有方仙客一人而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是方仙客只有—只手，又怎会是这两人呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我也知道他们绝不会是方仙客，所以我也猜不出他们是谁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论这两人是谁，咱们今天都少不得要经—番恶战了，我本以为回来后可以过两天太平日子，谁知一回来就遇上这么样两个人，早知如此，我宁可跟琵琶公主回龟兹国去了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又是个坟场，为什么每次有人找我打架时，总是要将我带到坟场上来?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他若想找你喝酒，自然会将你带到酒楼上去，可是他现在却想要你的命，自然只有在坟场上最方便。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这棺材若是为我准备的，就未免太小了些。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "笑脸黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "若是将你切成两半，岂非就正合适了么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_xiao_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你身材也和我差不多，这棺材装你也合适得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪最近棺材店生意兴隆，原来竟有人将棺材当凳子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知两位高姓大名?究竟是何意，是否和在下有什么过节?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摆酒上来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位竟是请咱们来喝酒的么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这地方没有什么好东西可奉敬两位。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请?请什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位难道要请我吃死人么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了这地方，不吃死人吃什么?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有趣有趣，实在有趣极了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "笑脸黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请请请，这人死了没多久，还新鲜得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们究竟……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香，你什么时候也学会吃死人了?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这人果然新鲜得很，滋味好极了，你也尝一块吧!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ku_lian_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "哭脸黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我早就知道这骗不过楚香帅的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这究竟是在搞什么鬼?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "小弟实在荒唐，但望胡兄恕罪。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有趣有趣，这真的有趣极了，我这一辈子都没有遇着如此有趣的事，你们两人实在有两下子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道两位一定被那些恶客纠缠得无法脱身，所以才想出这法子来，让两位解解闷，开开心。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "妙极妙极，这法子实在是妙绝天下，妙绝古今，除了嫂夫人，只怕天下再也没有第二个人能想出这法子来。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但她无论想得多妙，却还是瞒不过楚兄的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的确生了双利眼，可是我并不羡慕他，因为这样他反而会少了许多乐趣，永远都不会像我这么样开心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我生平虽然做过不少荒唐事，但坐在坟场里的棺材上喝酒，这倒真还是生平第一次。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡兄是否觉得有些不快?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "不快?我简直觉得愉快极了，和这地方一比，客栈里那间小屋子简直就闷得像棺材，和贤夫妇一比，那些大镖客简直就像是一群活鬼。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那时我虽戴着哭脸，但听见你替那位大镖客改的外号，几乎忍不住要笑出声来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "早知嫂夫人也听得见，那句话我就不敢说出来了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中人人都知道，当今武林有三大世家，其历史之悠久，名声之响亮，俱不在三大帮、七大派之下，而且每一家都有世代相传的武功秘笈，足以与少林的罗汉神拳、武当的两仪剑法分庭抗礼，只不过这三家门下子弟，俱都谨守家规，极少在江湖间走动而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "近数十年来，这三大武林世家，更是人才辈出，他们虽不常在江湖走动，但神龙偶现，所做所为，必是足以震惊天下的大事，譬如说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "譬如说，‘南宫世家’的南宫平，昔年就曾在一夜之间，扫平太行十八寨，而令横行天下四十年的太行贼寇，从此一蹶不振。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这已是五十年前的旧事了，昔年风采翩翩的南宫公子，也已在十年前便羽化登仙，近二三十年来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "近二三十年来，最轰动武林的大事，就是‘拥翠山庄’的李观鱼李老前辈，他在剑池的试剑石边，柬邀天下三十一位最著名的剑客，煮茶试剑，而李老前辈却以一口古鱼肠剑，九九八十一手凌风剑法，令三十一位名剑客都心悦诚服，推为天下第一剑客。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，这三大世家武功，虽然各有千秋，但近三十年来，却还是要以姑苏海碧山，‘拥翠山庄’为其中翘楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "李兄少年英俊，武功之高，更是江湖少见，若是在下猜得不错，想必定是‘拥翠山庄’的门下子弟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "惭愧，小弟不学无术，委实辜负了家门旧誉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "李兄太谦了，不知李兄和李观鱼李老前辈如何称呼?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "正是家父。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪贤伉俪风采如此照人，武林世家的子弟，果然是不同凡俗。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江山代有才人出，各领风骚数十年，非但‘拥翠山庄’的名誉，早已被我这种不肖子弟败坏，就连家父也久不敢再自居为天下第一剑客。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昔日在剑池旁陆羽茶亭中煮茶试剑的前辈剑客们，至今多已凋零，但江湖中的后起剑客，却多胜前人，据家父看来，当今天下的名家高手，单以剑法而论，就要数薛衣人薛大侠为天下第一。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "那只不过是李老前辈奖掖后进之意，在下虽也曾听说这位薛衣人的剑法奇幻瑰丽，不可方物，但无论经验、火候，比起李老前辈，无疑还是要差得很多，李兄又何必太谦。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，谦虚虽是美德，但若太谦虚，就反而假了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位有所不知，家父多年前便已不幸染上了一种不治之症，至今终年缠绵病榻，已有十年未曾提剑了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "光单以剑而论，虽推薛衣人，但若论机智武功，临敌决胜，普天之下，还有谁比得上楚香帅?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他虽然不错，但你也莫将他捧得太高，他可没有你如此谦虚的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至于说，近年来最轰动武林的大事，自然也得算楚香帅以一人之力，揭发了南宫灵和“妙僧”无花的阴谋，挽救了少林和丐帮的声誉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只不过是件小事而已，何足挂齿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你也不必太谦虚了，这件事若也算是小事，还有什么事才能算得上是大事?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若论机智武功，临敌决胜，固然无人能及楚香帅，但论胸怀磊落，洒脱不羁，又有谁能比得上胡铁花呢?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嫂夫人说对了，若以喝酒而论，才真没有人比得上我的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，普天之下，的确没有人比你醉得更快的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好小子，你竟敢在杜康门前卖五加皮?总有一天，我要和你拼一拼，看看究竟谁先倒下去。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杜康门前卖五加皮，这句话实在说得妙极，实在比孔夫子门前卖百家姓要生动活泼多了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "除了他这种酒鬼，谁也想不出这种话，这就叫三句不离本行。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位实在都是光明磊落、肝胆照人的好朋友，小弟能和两位相交，实是不胜之喜，实在恨不得和两位多盘桓几日。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们实在想请两位到‘拥翠山庄’去作平原十日之饮，那里的陆羽茶井，号称天下第三泉，烹茶固妙，制酒也不错。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早已听说‘拥翠山庄’背山面水，风物绝佳，早已巴不得能到那里去逛逛了，也好一睹天下第一剑客的风采。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只可惜我还要陪他去找几个人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下又何尝不想拜谒李老前辈，只恨俗务太多，这次只怕不能去了，好在来日方长，以后必定还有机会的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那实在太遗憾，我们家里有几个人正在急着想见见楚香帅哩!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你也不必问，想见你的人，一定是十六七岁的小姑娘，什么事也不懂，也不知从哪里听说什么‘盗帅夜留香’呀!‘流氓中的公子’呀!就一心认定你是个很了不起的人，李兄，我说的对不对?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那几位的确都是豆蔻年华的少女，但你若说她们不懂事，可就大大错了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那几位姑娘非但都是文武全才，聪明美丽，而且其中还有一位更是学富五车，才高八斗的扫眉才子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "哦!她叫什么名字?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的名字叫苏蓉蓉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    }
  ],
